### TYPOGRAPHY
Font: "Inter" — import from Google Fonts
Display font for hero headlines: "Inter" weight 900 or consider
a high-authority serif like "Playfair Display" for the main H1 only
if it reinforces institutional gravitas.

Scale:
- Display:  80px weight 900, line-height 1.0,  letter-spacing -0.04em
- H1:       64px weight 800, line-height 1.05, letter-spacing -0.03em
- H2:       44px weight 700, line-height 1.15, letter-spacing -0.02em
- H3:       30px weight 700, line-height 1.25, letter-spacing -0.01em
- H4:       22px weight 600, line-height 1.35
- Body LG:  19px weight 400, line-height 1.8
- Body:     16px weight 400, line-height 1.75
- Small:    14px weight 400, line-height 1.6
- XS:       12px weight 500, letter-spacing 0.05em
- Label:    11px weight 700, letter-spacing 0.12em, uppercase

On dark (Navy) backgrounds: text is Off-White (#F5F5F2)
On light (Off-White) backgrounds: text is Deep Navy (#0A1A2F)
Gold (#D4A857) is used ONLY for: accents, borders, hover states,
signal labels, and key CTAs — never for body text.

