### SPACING
Base grid: 8px
Section vertical padding: 112px
Card padding: 44px
Max content width: 1200px centered
Grid gutters: 28px

Border radius:
- Buttons:     10px
- Cards:       18px
- Intent Cards: 12px
- Inputs:      10px
- Badges/Pills: 100px
- Icon boxes:   12px

---

### MOTION & ANIMATION
Easing: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)
Default duration: 0.25s

Rules:
- Hover lift on cards: translateY(-4px), 0.25s ease
- Gold border on card hover: transition 0.2s ease
- Focus ring: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212,168,87,0.30)
- Page entrance: fade up — opacity 0→1, translateY(24px→0), stagger 0.1s
- Section entrance: Intersection Observer, animate on scroll
- Gold glow pulse on primary CTA: subtle box-shadow pulse 3s infinite
- All hover states: 0.2s ease minimum
- No jarring transitions — everything feels measured and deliberate

