### GLOBAL UI RULES
- Deep Navy (#0A1A2F) is the dominant background — lean into it
- Gold (#D4A857) is a signal — every use must be intentional and earned
- Off-White (#F5F5F2) is the text color on dark surfaces
- Readiness Green (#00C853) is ONLY for readiness state signals — never decorative
- No light backgrounds on full-page sections except Intent Cards
- No stock photography — system UI mockups and data visualizations only
- No rounded hero sections or colorful blobs — this is institutional, not startup
- Every shadow on dark surfaces uses rgba(0,0,0,0.40+) — deep, not soft
- All interactive elements: keyboard navigable, ARIA labeled
- Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio on all text
- This surface must feel heavier, more authoritative, and more premium
  than every other surface in the ecosystem
- The final result must look like the most serious B2B institutional
  platform ever built — federal authority, world-class execution

